com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.internal

Class DocumentServiceRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.internal.DocumentServiceRequest

  • public final class DocumentServiceRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    This is core Transport/Connection agnostic request to DocumentService. It is marked internal today. If needs arises for client to do no-serialized processing we can open this up to public.
